source.name: Maryland Female Labor Force Projections: 1970-2040
source.description:
Historical and Projected Female Labor Force in Maryland and its Jurisdictions 1970-2040.
Projected numbers are rounded to the nearest 10.
Prepared by the Maryland Department of Planning, April 2012.
